Class ShippingDock

java.lang.Object
Node<Order>
ShippingDock
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class ShippingDock
extends Node<Order>
Represents a shipping docks. Takes the input buffer and attempts to put the order into the output buffers. It checks the first buffer then the second one and keeps checking until it can place it in the queue.

Wil Simpson
